children.subject: Take 186 without 61c. You will be fine. To get a good grade in 186, just focus on learning the material presented in the class. They will give you plenty of time to digest each lecture.

history.content: Do we really need CS 61C to get a good grade in this class? I am a Data Science major and CS 61c is not an official prerequisite for the major.  I am considering this class since other database classes are being offered in a very small quantity. Thank you.
